{"tid":1799814,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會秘書處請議會秘書","createTime":"2019-12-27T08:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T15:16:20.000Z","uid":70194,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5212385c96e4c4c350fb85481845beb840e9705","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇巴打知個職系發展係點? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/sec/jobs/job20191206-cs-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fsec%2Fjobs%2Fjob20191206-cs-c.pdf&d=TEMpI0ru4fZij%2BnpPgfFHTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=9acad88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/sec/jobs/job20191206-cs-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處 (&quot;秘書處 &quot;)現正招聘 優秀人才出任議會秘書。在立法會行<br />\n政管理委員會的監督下，秘書處的使命是為立法會提供高效及專業的秘<br />\n書服務、資料研究及行政支援、提高公眾對立法會事務的認識，以及確<br />\n保提供處理市民申訴的有效途徑。<br />\n<br />\n主要職責<br />\n視乎個別職位，議會秘書的主要職責包括：<br />\n(a) 向立法會 及 其 轄下委員會 舉行的會議 提供秘書及支援 服務，包括<br />\n草擬資料文件及會議紀要；<br />\n(b) 統籌立法會與香港以外地方的其他議會組織的議會聯絡活動，以及<br />\n議員與外賓舉行的會議；<br />\n(c) 在立法會申訴制度下處理申訴；<br />\n(d) 為秘書處提供行政支援(例如人力資源管理、機構活動、辦公地方<br />\n及採購事宜等)；及<br />\n(e) 執行督導職務。<br />\n入職條件<br />\n應徵者應：<br />\n(a) 持有認可大學學位；<br />\n(b) 最少6年委員會工作、研究工作、處理申訴、翻譯、法律服務、機構<br />\n事務、人力資源管理、一般行政、採購或其他相關範疇的工作經驗。<br />\n曾任職香港特別行政區政府或公營機構而具備相關經驗者更佳。具<br />\n備少於6年經驗的申請人亦會被考慮，如獲受聘，入職薪金會定於<br />\n適當的薪點，並較此職位的起薪點為低；<br />\n(c) 極佳的中、英文講寫能力；<br />\n(d) 非常良好的溝通、分析及督導能力；及<br />\n(e) 處事成熟，並能獨立工作和承受工作壓力。<br />\n秘書處可制訂進一步的準則 ，以選出初步入選的申請人 。 初步入選的<br />\n申請人或須參加筆試。"},{"pid":"487288cea21da4ff4a3545509017af1bed0696b7","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"同埋係咪唔再直接recruit 高級議會秘書? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca88447f7cbca44ef4401efba01d1cc4f113ae2","tid":1799814,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2d917234894666606e0e26457623a32d783bd9a","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0acb431ba42bce4d0f764b45d8859a1bd0e445","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"推下先 冇人申請？"},{"pid":"0b150fb7307ba072c13deb82eb2bb963922223b5","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5756a33500aecc3e262d85a125d1d63bdffa67","tid":1799814,"uid":187774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"申請左"},{"pid":"74494e74454b6f5ccf93ad0433995f21e0832358","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d5756a33500aecc3e262d85a125d1d63bdffa67","tid":1799814,"uid":187774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"申請左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:27:58.000Z","msg":"知唔知個景點？上s 同上c 要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba56c4d9e358e76096c5f9b64cac0a0bc4399f0","tid":1799814,"uid":187774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"一如以往 <br />\nwritten test invitation出得好快<br />\n今個月16號下晝written test"},{"pid":"5d3d487fac7b70b22a8d8f2db24b4b32202fc059","tid":1799814,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba56c4d9e358e76096c5f9b64cac0a0bc4399f0","tid":1799814,"uid":187774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"一如以往 <br />\nwritten test inv